<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Login do Cliente | Megas Barato</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
            background: #f2f2f2;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 420px;
            margin: 60px auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
        }

        h2 {
            text-align: center;
            color: #e60000;
            font-size: 28px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .info {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-align: center;
            color: #000;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        label {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: bold;
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
        }

        input {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 14px;
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 18px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        button {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 15px;
            font-size: 20px;
            background: #e60000;
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        button:hover {
            background: #b30000;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 15px;
            color: #555;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <div class="container">
        <h2>Login do Cliente</h2>

        <div class="info">
            Por favor, faça login para poder comprar os megas diários da Vodacom.<br>
            Após a compra, envie o comprovativo da transferência.
        </div>

        <form action="/login" method="POST">
            <label for="telefone">Número de Telefone</label>
            <input type="text" id="telefone" name="telefone" placeholder="Ex: 84xxxxxxx" required>

            <button type="submit">Entrar</button>
        </form>

        <div class="footer">
            Megas Barato © 2025
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
